    <name>CUE 01 #81 Polecat Loop</name>
    <desc>Follow #81 Polecat Loop. First official segment here: Polecat Loop. Signpost: #81 Polecat Loop. Either direction allowed; follow map arrows. This is a navigation cue, not the full segment-credit audit.</desc>
  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="43.686343" lon="-116.221621">
    <name>CUE 02 Doe Ridge</name>
    <desc>Follow Doe Ridge. First official segment here: Doe Ridge. Either direction allowed; follow map arrows. This is a navigation cue, not the full segment-credit audit.</desc>
  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="43.681930" lon="-116.220503">
    <name>CUE 03 Quick Draw</name>
    <desc>Follow Quick Draw. First official segment here: Quick Draw. Either direction allowed; follow map arrows. This is a navigation cue, not the full segment-credit audit.</desc>
  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="43.678042" lon="-116.225980">
    <name>CUE 04 #81 Polecat Loop</name>
    <desc>Follow #81 Polecat Loop. First official segment here: Polecat Loop. Signpost: #81 Polecat Loop. SPECIAL MANAGEMENT: follow the signed one-way direction opposite official geometry. This is a navigation cue, not the full segment-credit audit.</desc>
  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="43.689720" lon="-116.219872">
